The Mountaineering and Adventure Sports Society unit of Sigaram Charitable Trust will be organising an outdoor event “Endurance and excellence” for college students, IT professionals, management staff and industrial staff at the Western Ghats, Udumalpet, February 27 onwards. Registrations close by February 24. They are also organising four ‘Himalayan expeditions’ from March 19 to May 31.

Trek routes are Indhrahar Pass, Bhrighu Lake, Deo Tibba base camp and Beaskund. For details, dial 9500 9000 67, 81100 70011;

email-massindia@gmail.com,sigaramtrust@gmail.com.
